Type: Package
Package: SummaryTables
Title: Publication-Ready Summary Tables for Jamovi
Version: 0.3.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Nour Edin", "Darwish", , "nouredindarwish@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0009-5527-4539"))
Description: Summary tables and descriptive statistics for jamovi. Create
    Table 1 with group comparisons, cross tabulations, and Likert-scale
    summaries. Supports continuous variables (mean, SD, median, IQR,
    range) and categorical variables (counts, percentages, frequencies).
    Statistical tests include t-test, ANOVA, Wilcoxon rank-sum,
    Kruskal-Wallis, Chi-square, Fisher's exact test, and Z test for
    proportions. Effect sizes include Cohen's d, Hedge's g, and
    standardized mean difference (SMD). Confidence intervals for means and
    proportions (Wilson, Clopper-Pearson, Wald, Agresti-Coull, Jeffreys).
    P values with adjustment methods including Bonferroni,
    Benjamini-Hochberg, Holm, and others. Export tables to Word (.docx).
    Missing data handling with customizable labels. Journal formatting
    (JAMA, The Lancet, NEJM, QJE). Per-variable control over statistics,
    tests, and methods. 16 languages. Built on the 'gtsummary' package.
